Class KeyWordList

  • java.lang.Object
    • KeyWordList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.String>

    public class KeyWordList
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.String>
    This is a wrapper class meant to store the keywords. It's current implementation uses an arrayList. We have created our own class, the KeyWordList, which is used to store a list of keywords. This class is very simple, and was designed to facilitate the integration of new features in the future. Currently it simply wraps an array of Strings.

    Yasha
